\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Academy of Sound Engineering is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC.\line \line The Higher Certificate in Screen Media programme was deferred during the Accreditation Committee meeting of 05 and 06 October 2011 for the following reasons\'3A\line \line 1. The institution must ensure that sufficient information for this programme is submitted\'2C indicating levels\'2C credits and learning components of this qualification as well as the outcomes and assessments\'2C and that this is also accurately captured in the SAQA qualification document.\line 2. The institution must indicate how all students will be provided with or have access to relevant facilities for the specialised needs of the programme\'2C e.g. appropriate cameras. \cell \pard 

